Hair by @andrita

Styling by @meccajw 
Nails by @nailglam

node.text:
This day was a DREAM COME TRUE for my sister and I! 😭🥺🥰 This was the day we went to pretty much ALL of our local @UltaBeauty stores 😂 to see our @MelaninHaircare products in-store for THE FIRST TIME! 😭🙏🏾❤️❤️

Firstly, yall sold them shelves OUUTTT!! 🤣😂 We were barely able to catch any of our babies in action!! 😂😂🙏🏾 But we were just as excited to see those empty shelves, as we were to see the products!! 💯💯😭👏🏾🤗

Meet my big sister, Taffeta! She is my biggest supporter and protector, always has been since I was born (fun fact, she asked my mom and dad for a baby sister!! So if you like my natural hair tips, you have her to thank for them! 🤣🤣💯💯)

Anyway, we can’t thank you all enough for believing in us, and in our dream for @MelaninHaircare!! 🥰🥰 This has been such an incredible journey and we are JUST getting started! 🥳💃🏾 There is so much more to come, just you wait!! 😆😝🙏🏾 XOXO!! We love you #MelaninBae thank YOU! 🥰🤗❤️✨✨✨✨

ps. Be sure to check your local @UltaBeauty stores as your favorite @MelaninHaircare goodies have been RESTOCKED!! 🥳😝💃🏾✨ #MelaninHaircare #MelaninBae

node.text:
Full Video Linked In Bio! 🥰🤗 I’m really attached to my hair. Whether it’s on or OFF my head, it impacts my self-image, or rather, my self-image impacts IT. 💯

I’ve been through my own personal hell these past 7 months - and maybe someday soon I’ll sit down and chat about it - but my world was completely flipped upside down.

I had to deconstruct my life, my loyalties, my responsibilities, and my self-worth. I was torn down and honestly didn’t know how I could ever build myself back up again. What I thought I knew to be a constant and reliable truth in my life - was gone. Cue the panic attacks.

And so I worked. I loved hard on my children. I loved hard on my family. I loved hard on myself. I rebuilt my heart, my mindset, my space, my limitations, and healed from the inside out. And I found out that I’m so much stronger and more capable than I ever thought possible. And turns out, with my new changes, my mental health also improved for the better - go figure. 🙄

This was more than a hair cut to me. I NEEDED THIS. I NEEDED to see myself as I felt inside. It was suffocating and I was no longer someone who needed the extra length, the extra baggage to define her. I DEFINE ME by BEING ME. And just like I no longer wanted to carry MY extra baggage  with me into the future, the hair could kick it too.✌🏾
⠀
Also, while yes - it IS just hair, it will always simultaneously be MORE. It’s inconsequential because it’s gonna grow back, but at the same time, it shapes HOW you view YOURSELF on a day to day basis, and for that reason if your SELF-IMAGE doesn’t align, it can be weighty.

So. 🥵😆 Thank you for your loving comments and support on my hair cut video! 🙏🏾🥰 I would’ve been ecstatic for my cut no matter what, but knowing y’all got my back when I sometimes make drastic moves is really cool to know. XO! 😘❤️ #naptural85 #naturalhair #naturalhairgoals #naturalhairstyles #thecutlife #shortnaturalhairstyle #shortnaturalhair #shortnaturalhairstyles #naturalhaircommunity #naturalhairdaily #type4hair #type4natural #type4naturalistas #type4hairstyles #type4ahair #thebc #thebigchop #thebigchop✂️ #transitioninghair #transitioningtonatural

Featuring a chic, fun pattern with a double-sided print, the Original Melanin Haircare Lux T-Shirt Hair Towel is as cute as it is practical! 😍👏🏾❤️✨

The NEW #MelaninHaircare LUX T-Shirt Hair Towel is available NOW!! [Ships Friday July 9] 🥳🙌🏾💃🏾 Secure yours exclusively at www.MelaninHaircare.com and The Melanin Haircare App! 🤳🏾🛍😘 #MelaninHaircare #MelaninBae⁠

✨NEW TINGS Have ARRIVED!! 🤩✨ [1/2] Introducing the NEW @MelaninHaircare XL Shower Mirror! 😍🎉🪞Our lightweight, fogless, shatterproof shower mirror is sleek, minimalist, and classic! 💎 Boasting an impressive 10” x 10” frame 📐 and giving you more than enough viewing space to see your entire head of ✨beautiful✨ hair without feeling restricted! 🥰👏🏾 Did we mention it has fogless technology? 😉😆🎊⁠
⁠
Featuring discreet drainage holes in bottom of the frame for effortless upkeep, ensuring that no water is stored 💦 and strong suction cup adhesion 🩹 for easy rearranging that won’t damage your walls!👩🏾‍🍳💋 Sealed with the minimal “Melanin” logo kiss, this is sure to become your new favorite shower accessory! 🚿🙌🏾🥳✨⁠
⁠
The NEW #MelaninHaircare XL Shower Mirror is available NOW!! [Ships Friday July 9] 🥳🙌🏾💃🏾 Secure yours exclusively at www.MelaninHaircare.com and The Melanin Haircare App! 🤳🏾🛍😘 #MelaninHaircare #MelaninBae
